outputs.description: CLOSED N Program Promotion and Support

Government policy makers, partners, donors and international and local public are informed about children's issues and UNICEFprogramme activities to support them across crisis affected population of Iraq. These informational activities will help to promoteequity-focused policies, legislation and development plans/investments, and ensure the rights of all Iraqi  children are protected.Additionally, programme focused communication will enhance social and behavior change to achieve specific outcomes enhance peacebuilding and resilience.

Furtherance of UNICEF global focus and change initiatives on increased accountability, Enterprise Risk Management, promotecoherence and harmonization of business practices in operations across UNICEF IRAQ Country Office.
